name: Komatsuzaki Rui - Danganronpa Artist Style
description:
A LoRA replicating the Art Style of Komatsuzaki Rui. Trained on NAI.

Works well with most anime models and with a weight of 0.8-1.

Please use Highres fix and an upscaler to get similar results. Upscaling is required so the eyes don't look like shit if you're not doing a close shot.

If you like this LoRA, please let a review!

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
